-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IGMS\" title=\"IGM Biosciences, Inc.\">IGMS</a></span>) since I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4638339-igm-biosciences-what-causes-high-short-interest-in-this-ticker\">covered</a> it in October last year. But mostly, the stock has done well \u2013 it is up 25% right now and was even higher at some points. This is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742059-igm-biosciences-dizzying-number-of-pivots", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 18:32:47"}, {"id": "4742058", "title": "Fossil Group: Recent Surge Calls Attention To Interesting Turnaround Situation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876158370/image_876158370.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close-up of businessman outdoors checking the time\" data-id=\"876158370\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876158370/image_876158370.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876158370/image_876158370.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876158370/image_876158370.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876158370/image_876158370.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876158370/image_876158370.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876158370/image_876158370.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876158370/image_876158370.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876158370/image_876158370.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\"