ed positively, with Q3'24 recording a revenue increase of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1873240976/image_1873240976.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742054-enovix-buckle-up-near-term-commercialization-will-bring-the-company-forward", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 18:12:47"}, {"id": "4742052", "title": "Vuzix: Positioned As The Go-To OEM Supplier For The Exploding Smart Glasses Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Smart glasses with proection on the screen. VR virtual reality and AR augmented reality technology concept.\" data-id=\"1341285836\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Bet_Noire/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Vuzix Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VUZI\" title=\"Vuzix Corporation\">VUZI</a></span>) is a $190 million designer and manufacturer of smart glasses and augmented reality tech. It serves the industry as a manufacturer of waveguides, and is thus positioned as a key supplier to OEMs. With so many</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1341285836/image_1341285836.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742052-vuzix-positioned-as-the-go-to-oem-supplier-for-the-exploding-smart-glasses-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 18:10:53"}, {"id": "4742051", "title": "SCHY: Makes An Excellent International Companion To SCHD", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498147203/image_1498147203.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"beautiful pink savings pig on top of a wooden board\" data-id=\"1498147203\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"841px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498147203/image_1498147203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498147203/image_1498147203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498147203/image_1498147203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498147203/image_1498147203.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498147203/image_1498147203.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498147203/image_1498147203.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498147203/image_1498147203.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https:/